file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0 info: title: TickHistory description: >- TickHistory provides dynamic access to historical tick data for a specific security for specific dates or date range. version: 1.0.0 servers: - url: https://api-sandbox.factset.com/bulk-documents/tickhistory security: - FactSetApiKey: [] - FactSetOAuth2: [] paths: /v1/request-files: get: tags: - Request-files summary: Returns the requestId and status description: >- Try it Out - references a Sandbox environment to simulate live reponses.

**In Sandbox** data available from 20210101 to 20210131. Current date data is not available.

PROD has data from 20120101 to current date &

**available IDs is limited to..**

US Equity - IBM-USA, F-USA, AAPL-USA, GOOG-USA

ASX - CBA-ASX, BHP-ASX

LSE - HSBA-LON, VOD-LON

Tokyo - 7203-TKS, 4307-TKS

Swiss - NESN-SWX, COTN-SWX

Singapore - J36-SES &

Hong Kong - 700-HKG

parameters: - $ref: '#/components/parameters/ticker' - $ref: '#/components/parameters/iso_code' - $ref: '#/components/parameters/fields' - $ref: '#/components/parameters/start_date' - $ref: '#/components/parameters/end_date' responses: '200': description: Successs content: application/json: schema: $ref: '#/components/schemas/Request-FilesResponse' examples: default200ResponseExample: $ref: '#/components/examples/sampleRequest-FilesResponse' '400': description: Bad Request content: application/json: schema: $ref: '#/components/schemas/Request-Filestatus' examples: default400ReponseExample: $ref: '#/components/examples/Request-FileErrorDetails' /v1/get-files: get: tags: - Get-files summary: Returns the files from tickhistory endpoint for the specified date range parameters: - $ref: '#/components/parameters/requestId' - $ref: '#/components/parameters/_paginationLimit' - $ref: '#/components/parameters/_paginationOffset' responses: '200': description: >- Success

**To download the output file copy the response url in a browser** content: application/json: schema: $ref: '#/components/schemas/Get-FilesResponse' examples: default200ResponseExample: $ref: '#/components/examples/sampleGet-FilesResponse' '400': description: Bad Request content: application/json: schema: $ref: '#/components/schemas/Get-FilesStatus' examples: default400ReponseExample: $ref: '#/components/examples/Get-FileErrorDetails' components: securitySchemes: FactSetOAuth2: type: oauth2 flows: clientCredentials: tokenUrl: https://auth.factset.com/as/token.oauth2 scopes: {} FactSetApiKey: type: http scheme: basic parameters: ticker: name: ticker in: query description: >- any ticker.

**Either ticker(s) + iso_code (OR) product is allowed**

**NOTE**:Only one identifier can be requested per request required: false schema: type: string examples: fieldname1: value: IBM,F,AAPL,GOOG summary: US Equity fieldname2: value: CBA,BHP summary: ASX fieldname3: value: HSBA,VOD summary: LSE fieldname4: value: 7203,4307 summary: Tokyo fieldname5: value: NESN,COTN summary: Swiss fieldname6: value: J36 summary: Singapore fieldname7: value: 700 summary: HongKong iso_code: name: iso_code in: query description: >- iso_code.

ticker(s) + iso_code

**Does not support multiple iso_codes**

required: false schema: type: string examples: fieldname1: value: USA summary: US Equity fieldname2: value: AUS summary: ASX fieldname3: value: LON summary: LSE fieldname4: value: TKS summary: Tokyo fieldname5: value: SWX summary: Swiss fieldname6: value: SES summary: Singapore fieldname7: value: HKG summary: HongKong fields: name: fields in: query description: >- Fields for which data is requested. Refer Output fileds list. for available fields.

**In trial default=all fields** required: false schema: type: string default: '*' examples: fieldname1: value: '*' summary: all fields fieldname2: value: ask summary: single field fieldname3: value: ticker,ask,msgtype summary: multiple fields start_date: name: start_date in: query description: >- The date for (or from which) the data is required

**In Sandbox, data available from 1st to 31st Jan'21 only** required: true schema: type: string format: date minimum: -30 examples: exactDate: value: '2021-01-01' summary: Files from Jan 1,2021 end_date: name: end_date in: query description: >- The date to which data is required

**In Sandbox, data available from 1st to 31st Jan'21 only** required: true schema: type: string format: date examples: exactDate: value: '2021-01-31' summary: Files until Jan 31,2021 requestId: name: requestId in: query description: >- RequestId returned by request-files endpoint to poll and collect results of the query required: true schema: type: string _paginationLimit: name: _paginationLimit in: query description: Specifies the maximum number of results to return per response page required: false schema: type: integer default: 20 _paginationOffset: name: _paginationOffset in: query description: >- Specifies the starting point for pagination. This parameter is used to identify the beginning of next set of results required: false schema: type: integer default: 0 schemas: Request-FilesResponse: type: object properties: requestId: description: a unique identification# for the query requested type: string status: description: The status of the query type: string Get-FilesResponse: type: object properties: status: description: The status of the request type: string request: description: >- Returns the query parameters, user credentials (name & serial number) type: string requestTimestamp: description: Timestamp of when request was made type: string format: date-time updateTimestamp: description: ':"Timestamp when the file was last updated"' type: string format: date-time data: type: array items: $ref: '#/components/schemas/data' meta: type: array items: $ref: '#/components/schemas/meta' data: title: Data description: Array of data objects type: object properties: fileName: description: Name of the file(s) generated for the query requested type: string url: description: Download link for the TickHistory file with requested parameters type: string meta: title: Meta description: Array of metadata objects type: object properties: pagination: $ref: '#/components/schemas/pagination' partial: $ref: '#/components/schemas/partial' pagination: title: Pagination description: List of pagination objects type: object properties: total: description: Total number of files the API returns for a particular query type: integer is EstimatedTotal: description: >- Boolean value that represents whether the total count of files returned is exact or an estimate. This is defaulted to “False” as the API should always return the exact count type: boolean limit: description: Number of results returned per page type: integer offset: description: >- The flag indicating the position in the results array if additional results are available beyond the default value or the value in paginationLimit parameter (if used). This value is passed in the _paginationOffset parameter to retreieve subsequent results type: integer partial: title: IsPartial description: >- If the value is true, it indicates additional results are available. False represents that this is the last set of results for this request. type: object properties: isPartial: type: boolean Request-Filestatus: title: Request-FileStatus description: status of request or Error response object returned in status property type: object properties: id: type: string details: $ref: '#/components/schemas/Request-FileErrorDetails' Request-FileErrorDetails: type: object title: Request-Files Error Messages properties: Permission Error: type: array items: type: string description: Error message when user is not subscribed to the TickHistory product Param Error: type: array items: type: string description: when the parameters passed in the query are incorrect or missing startDate: type: array items: type: string description: startDate must be < 0 endDate: type: array items: type: string description: endDate must be < 0 Get-FilesStatus: title: Get-FilesStatus description: status of request or Error response object returned in status property type: object properties: id: type: string details: $ref: '#/components/schemas/Get-FilesErrorDetail' Get-FilesErrorDetail: type: object title: Get-Files Error Messages properties: not_authorized_tickers: type: array items: type: string description: query with partial tickers, products or exchanges not subscribed to _paginationLimit: type: array items: type: string description: _paginationLimit must be <=500 _paginationOffset: type: array items: type: string description: _paginationoffset must be an integer examples: sampleRequest-FilesResponse: summary: sample Response value: requestId: '**(Example)** 27b4923f-86dd-4b8b-89ac-dfc3a26fa786 **(Example)**' status: Submitted sampleGet-FilesResponse: summary: sample Response value: status: Completed **(Example)** request: >- type=fetch&fields=*,date&filter=date:20190220,ticker:FDS&user=XXXXXXXX&serial=XXXXX requestTimestamp: '2020-10-23 03:38:02' updateTimestamp: '2020-10-23 03:41:39' data: -
